Path: This week in Nu #76
Content:
More scripts were added to the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts] Nu script collection
RReverser did a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2983] few fixes to the WASI build
jonathandturner moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2984] filesize to use bigint
, fixed a few 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3007] issues with 
``ps``
fdncred fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2988] build break caused by a sysinfo update
, standardized some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2992] file size logic
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2993] README to include contributors
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3000] more internal value type helpers
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/3006] sysinfo
,
andrasio improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2997] ``to md``
 markdown support
